  <project_license>MIT</project_license>
  
  <name>GitHub Puller</name>
  <summary>Batch download GitHub repositories</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>GitHub Puller is a simple and efficient GTK4 application for downloading multiple GitHub repositories at once.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Download multiple repositories with a single action</li>
      <li>Modern GNOME-integrated user interface</li>
      <li>Support for batch operations</li>
      <li>Organized directory structure</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
